Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:50.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ほら　ほらおいで　{\c&H000000&}見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}急ぎた{\c&H000000&}くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:56.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}いいよ　{\c&H000000&}慣れない傷も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:01.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}その笑顔が{\c&H000000&}見たいから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:07.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}願い　願え　{\c&H000000&}終わらせないで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:12.03,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}君と八百万{\c&H000000&}のぬくもりを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:17.29,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}まとい　捧ぎ　{\c&H000000&}あらがい抱くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.96,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}何度でも呼{\c&H000000&}んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}蝶結びア{\c&H000000&}ミュレット
