Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:42.15,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}后方的正面　{\c&H000000&}抓住这只手的会是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来　来　过来吧　{\c&H000000&}来跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}比起{\c&H000000&}犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:50.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来　来　过来吧　{\c&H000000&}去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:51.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}着急{\c&H000000&}更占多数
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:56.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}没事的 {\c&H000000&}不习惯的伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:01.96,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也希望看到{\c&H000000&}那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:07.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}请求　许愿吧　{\c&H000000&}不要让其停下
